{"tid":1604342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[普天同㷫] 我已經知聽日會發生咩事","createTime":"2019-09-30T02:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:55:13.000Z","uid":218313,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d5fb294ab5ad32b14a7990d42573786427647f8b","tid":1604342,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"咁高興既日子, 對家一定已經安排好, 最少安排一定會係咁:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1&gt; 一朝早(約十點開始), 狗鐵車站, 高調安排狗狗亂尻check 人捉人<br />\n2&gt; 狗鐵亦好可能十二點停駛<br />\n3&gt; 巴士會check人<br />\n4&gt; 集合地點會有重兵, 唔俾你聚人<br />\n5&gt; 聚左人都好, 會先退--&gt;後圍--&gt;再捕</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">但係, 咁係唔會令我地驚架!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講左好多次, 唔好只係為啖氣出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班出到黎又跟大隊尻坐尻企係一D 用都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地已經唔係安全遊行<br />\n每個人都要醒覺<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">出黎係要有目標/目的!</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日目的只有一個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">普天同㷫, 賀佢老母</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要全港九都係我地既人<br />\n要全港九都賀佢老母, 貼滿街招, 美國旗海飄揚<br />\n要話俾佢地知我地唔撚會放棄<br />\n落尻佢面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以, 我強烈建議:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1&gt; 和理非唔該帶備足夠單張(一人最少50-100張), 行過地方就貼佢老母</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">2&gt;  <strong><ins>不要打陣地戰/不要打陣地戰/不要打陣地戰</ins></strong>, SET 左RB 就走!<br />\n      隊伍要快速移動! 唔好停!! 全港九走走走</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">3&gt;  唔好落單! 最少100人一Group</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">4&gt;  打狗救人!! 一個不能少!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望聽日大家武運昌隆!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警死全家!! DKLM 目家鏟!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推</span></span>"},{"pid":"19bfbbf283a9ee475f3a4b11d97014bb203a68cb","tid":1604342,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a458d713a34b54c657c7768bbe609bb2d88987d","tid":1604342,"uid":284630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"預左10月1號會好似929銅鑼灣咁樣<br />\n不過係全香港18區, 每幾條街都有一隊狗咁樣<br />\n<br />\n其實3萬個差佬, 真係全部洗晒腦?<br />\n少少10月1號既部署都冇風聲漏出黎, 真係好恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47516c22bf46b03ef185e1c90522b3f5752d554e","tid":1604342,"uid":218313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4a458d713a34b54c657c7768bbe609bb2d88987d","tid":1604342,"uid":284630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"預左10月1號會好似929銅鑼灣咁樣<br />\n不過係全香港18區, 每幾條街都有一隊狗咁樣<br />\n<br />\n其實3萬個差佬, 真係全部洗晒腦?<br />\n少少10月1號既部署都冇風聲漏出黎,